{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-css-foundations-projects/css-foundations-exercise-d","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"top-learn-css-foundations-projects","demoType":null,"title":"Osnovna vežba za CSS D","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za ovu vežbu, dali smo vam gotov fajl HTML, stoga ćete samo morati da uredite fajl CSS. Za ovu vežbu, važnije je razumeti kako funkcioniše serijsko povezivanje selektora nego kako dodati svojstva elementa.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Trebalo bi da vidiš <code>width</code> od <code>300px</code> u klasi elemenata <code>avatar</code> i <code>proportioned</code>.</li>\n<li>Trebaće ti da joj dodeliš visinu kako bi zadržala prvobitni kvadratni omjer (nemoj direktno kreirati vrijednost visine za jedan piksel!).</li>\n<li>Trebaće ti da joj dodeliš elemente sa klasama <code>avatar</code> i <code>distorted</code> <code>width</code> od <code>200px</code>.</li>\n<li>Trebaće ti da joj dodeliš <code>height</code> dvostruku njene širine.</li>\n</ol>\n</section>","id":"63ee3ff1381756f9716727f2","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":25,"helpCategory":"Odin","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-css-foundations-projects/css-foundations-exercise-d"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"stylescss","ext":"css","name":"styles","contents":"","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["styles.css"]},{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <title>Chaining Selectors</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\">\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <!-- Use the classes BELOW this line -->\n    <div>\n      <img class=\"avatar proportioned\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/odin-project/css-foundations/css-foundations-01.jpg\" alt=\"Two kittens on a blanket.\">\n      <img class=\"avatar distorted\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/odin-project/css-foundations/css-foundations-02.jpg\" alt=\"A cute kitten in the woods.\">\n    </div>\n    <!-- Use the classes ABOVE this line -->\n    <div>\n      <img class=\"original proportioned\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/odin-project/css-foundations/css-foundations-01.jpg\" alt=\"Two kittens on a blanket.\">\n      <img class=\"original distorted\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/odin-project/css-foundations/css-foundations-02.jpg\" alt=\"A cute kitten in the woods.\">\n    </div>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imaš <code>width</code> od <code>300px</code> u klasi objekata <code>avatar</code> i <code>proportioned</code>.</p>","testString":"const style = new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getStyle(`.avatar.proportioned`) || new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getStyle(`.proportioned.avatar`);\nassert(style?.width === '300px');"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imaš dužinu od <code>auto</code> u klasi objekata <code>avatar</code> i <code>proportioned</code>.</p>","testString":"const style = new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getStyle(`.avatar.proportioned`) || new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getStyle(`.proportioned.avatar`)\nassert(style?.height === 'auto');"},{"text":"<p>Treba koristiti selektor serijske veze u klasi objekata <code>avatar</code> i <code>proportioned</code>.</p>","testString":"const style = new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getStyle(`.avatar.proportioned`) || new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getStyle(`.proportioned.avatar`);\nassert(style);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imaš <code>width</code> od <code>200px</code> u klasi objekata <code>avatar</code> i <code>distorted</code>.</p>","testString":"const style = new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getStyle(`.avatar.distorted`) || new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getStyle(`.distorted.avatar`);\nassert(style?.width === '200px');"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da koristite selektor serijskog povezivanja u klasi objekata <code>avatar</code> i <code>distorted</code>.</p>","testString":"const style = new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getStyle(`.avatar.distorted`) || new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getStyle(`.distorted.avatar`);\nassert(style);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imaš dva puta širine <code>height</code> u elementu <code>avatar</code> i <code>distorted</code>.</p>","testString":"const style = new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getStyle(`.avatar.distorted`) || new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getStyle(`.distorted.avatar`);\nassert(style?.height === '400px');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/the-odin-project/#top-learn-css-foundations-projects","dashedName":"css-foundations-exercise-d","certification":"the-odin-project","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"top-learn-css-foundations-projects","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-css-foundations-projects/css-foundations-exercise-e","prevChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-css-foundations-projects/css-foundations-exercise-c","id":"63ee3ff1381756f9716727f2","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":25,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"styles","ext":"css","contents":".container .text {\n  background-color: yellow;\n  color: red;\n  font-size: 20px;\n  text-align: center;\n}","history":["styles.css"],"fileKey":"stylescss"},{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <title>Descendant Combinator</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\">\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <